(69, 1, '2018-10-31 04:34:47', '2018-10-31 04:34:47', 'Today, October 1<sup>st</sup>, marks Sensor Networks, Inc’s 4<sup>th</sup>Anniversary. We’re super excited and pleased to celebrate our amazing growth trajectory. Four years ago, we started with just three employees, a 1,200 square feet office (111 square meters), zero customers and a blank piece of paper for our sole but non-existent product offering.<u></u><u></u>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"CToWUd a6T\" tabindex=\"0\" src=\"https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/lKjr9XX5EhJpGRu1cng4ocNRUz-PHoUN_cyJX4F1osRQ55lvo4tdiHxMpOhuXbl_oY3Qwo61jB9JjRHnYXiJny4UmI_9-zDJfUshxY_4vTUiUowQim_wNRDyq4rIl6uYbFz2tIy6O9mvJ2UfjkQ-VZp3SYVWompw3DaNpPgtNr11gOvqV87OvhnZugddCZabLN6GT1V3eBY=s0-d-e1-ft#https://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/4630407/hubfs/Newsletter_Fall_2018/SNI%20Birthday.jpg?t=1538343243222&amp;width=300&amp;name=SNI%20Birthday.jpg\" alt=\"Sensor Networks, Inc turns four.\" width=\"300\" align=\"right\" />Today, we have 45 employees, over 12,000 square feet (1,110 square meters) of office, lab &amp; factory space, dozens of products, seven pending patents, hundreds of satisfied customers and four remote employees at offices in Houston, Hong Kong and Osaka. For the original three employees: Mark Feydo, Jim Barshinger and Bruce Pellegrino, it’s been an amazing and fun ride.<u></u><u></u>\r\n\r\nWe thank the 42 who have joined us since October 1st, 2014, and are grateful to our wonderful suppliers, dealers and customers for their support as we look forward to the future and continue to leverage our strengths and prior investments in people, equipment &amp; technology.<u></u><u></u>\r\n\r\nIn celebration of our 4th anniversary we’re launching a new newsletter format. We hope you find this new interactive newsletter more engaging and educational. Please be sure to add this new email address to your <i>Safe Sender</i> list.', 'Sensor Networks, Inc Happy Birthday SNI', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sensor-networks-inc-happy-birthday-sni', '', '', '2018-10-31 04:34:47', '2018-10-31 04:34:47', '', 0, 'http://sn.elephantintheboardroom.com.au/blog/?p=69', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(24, 1, '2018-10-03 01:46:32', '2018-10-03 01:46:32', '<h2><strong>Corrosion &amp; Prevention Conference 2017</strong></h2>\nThe Corrosion and Prevention Conference is the largest Corrosion Conference and Exhibition in the Southern Hemisphere. The 2017 Conference was held in Sydney and the conference comprised a program of keynote presentations and technical papers under a range of categories.\n\nSN Integrity\'s Nestor Sequera presented on smarter solutions for your complex asset integrity challenges. Specifically Nestors speech covered \"Deployment of Smart Ultrasonic Sensors\" for internal corrosion monitoring using the internet of things [IoT].\n\n<strong>The Agenda:</strong>\n\n<strong>A Historical Overview</strong>\n• Tell Tales\n• Intrusive Monitoring: Corrosion Coupons &amp; Probes\n• Ultrasonic D Meter\n• Evolution of TML’s /CML’s\n\n<strong>Non-Intrusive Smart Ultrasonic Sensors System</strong>\n• Details: principle, Internet of Things (IoT’s)\n• Smart Ultrasonic Sensors Attributes\nField Deployment (3 cases)\n\n<strong>Conclusions</strong>\n\nDownload the paper, presentation &amp; pictures below.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>Download the 2017 Corrosion &amp; Prevention </b><strong>Conference Presentation <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"/blog/wp-content/themes/snintegrity/images/pdf/presentation.pdf\" download=\"\">here</a></span>.</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Download the Paper <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"/images/pdf/nestor.pdf\" download=\"\">here</a></span>: </strong>“Deployment of Smart Ultrasonic Sensors for Internal Corrosion Monitoring using Internet of Things”.\n\n&nbsp;\n<div><strong>Guest Speaker</strong></div>\n<div>Nestor Sequera</div>\n<div>SN Integrity Pty. Ltd.</div>\n<div>Adelaide, Australia</div>\n<div>nestor@snintegrity.com.au</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-26\" src=\"http://sn.elephantintheboardroom.com.au/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/CONF-131117-95-1-min-300x200