(81, 1, '2018-10-31 04:56:56', '2018-10-31 04:56:56', 'Today, October 1<sup>st</sup>, marks Sensor Networks, Inc’s 4<sup>th</sup>Anniversary. We’re super excited and pleased to celebrate our amazing growth trajectory. Four years ago, we started with just three employees, a 1,200 square feet office (111 square meters), zero customers and a blank piece of paper for our sole but non-existent product offering.<u></u><u></u>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"CToWUd a6T\" tabindex=\"0\" src=\"https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/lKjr9XX5EhJpGRu1cng4ocNRUz-PHoUN_cyJX4F1osRQ55lvo4tdiHxMpOhuXbl_oY3Qwo61jB9JjRHnYXiJny4UmI_9-zDJfUshxY_4vTUiUowQim_wNRDyq4rIl6uYbFz2tIy6O9mvJ2UfjkQ-VZp3SYVWompw3DaNpPgtNr11gOvqV87OvhnZugddCZabLN6GT1V3eBY=s0-d-e1-ft#https://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/4630407/hubfs/Newsletter_Fall_2018/SNI%20Birthday.jpg?t=1538343243222&amp;width=300&amp;name=SNI%20Birthday.jpg\" alt=\"Sensor Networks, Inc turns four.\" width=\"300\" align=\"right\" />Today, we have 45 employees, over 12,000 square feet (1,110 square meters) of office, lab &amp; factory space, dozens of products, seven pending patents, hundreds of satisfied customers and four remote employees at offices in Houston, Hong Kong and Osaka. For the original three employees: Mark Feydo, Jim Barshinger and Bruce Pellegrino, it’s been an amazing and fun ride.<u></u><u></u>\r\n\r\nWe thank the 42 who have joined us since October 1st, 2014, and are grateful to our wonderful suppliers, dealers and customers for their support as we look forward to the future and continue to leverage our strengths and prior investments in people, equipment &amp; technology.<u></u><u></u>\r\n\r\nIn celebration of our 4th anniversary we’re launching a new newsletter format. We hope you find this new interactive newsletter more engaging and educational. Please be sure to add this new email address to your <i>Safe Sender</i> list.\r\n<h1>Meet Mark Matthews<u></u><u></u></h1>\r\n<div id=\"m_2556802078134433081hs_cos_wrapper_module_153728813568440_\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"CToWUd\" src=\"https://ci5.googleusercontent.com/proxy/P9nofy5y31tuqmREvgNnKx3YZX_2Zg8vTT7NAqFk5bi3QJB-dcFPNywYzebz1-jyXvdJSbleHu6adXRHEmhRfsIZ8CKB3hEVO0kERJdNuIrUFc1Gu2LteftUg3iZfcObFl5ME6qqVKdiRq1_2D0W1yMdpfCUbdKW9oMC6teQFk04XqAPK-KHKzJiLUer1rGc_FIcZA=s0-d-e1-ft#https://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/4630407/hubfs/Newsletter_Fall_2018/MarkMatthews.png?t=1538343243222&amp;width=148&amp;name=MarkMatthews.png\" alt=\"Mark Matthews\" width=\"148\" align=\"right\" />SNI is pleased to announce a new addition to our ever-growing team. Mark Matthews joined Sensor Networks, Inc. on July 1st, 2018. He is a RVI veteran sales professional and has over 20 years related experience at companies like Everest VIT, GE Inspection Technologies and Hexagon Metrology. Contact Mark at <a href=\"mailto:matthews@sensornetworksinc.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">matthews@sensornetworksinc.com</a><wbr /> or 610.425.2210 for a RVI demo or application consultation.\r\n\r\nMark will also be attending and presenting at SPRINT Robotics’ <strong>1st World Conference for Inspection and Maintenance Robotics, </strong>Nov 13-14 in Galveston, TX.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a href=\"https://resources.sensornetworkscorp.com/e2t/c/*W34K0sK4qwTvXW3NXbmN4FJ56d0/*W5MgL-C8PGXJxW8DzCGV44XCG90/5/f18dQhb0S1Wf7Bf-z4V1x40_1MNfhkVnZ1x-4YF3MTW5RkgSm45gNB8W7yPYJH3H1yhmW7n0lFj89hk-yW4z7qn25Qgdq8N4qDRn1V3bXfN8cs-NspYwbpVwSKFt8_8T-WN6YnfmSBs3cWW88JsjS7yYbNTW7kSyBs5gpTXfW79PXhK8hpkZKVlRkD-76MJSCN7k2cmv68YBmW21VWx-5lkYr3W36LDVZ7zZDxDN2pdPDb31lJ0W25SmXG5tdzhjW6Br_F41G-XBQW5HYPkw30YWw9W4N6C-p7xQQyqW1l5M-W536F-CW2p27r-5cXQ-KW3jj9Zc4N5kyWW4GW89-5GnLp_W1H0_dQ5cWkF8W8d9sYC272-93W2qt74T81LPYnW1qbKJd91zNMxW16fQtL2B4z0sW3CxTn_8yDXHZW5CqRYb7vy-hmW4TmsjH7Kwj6xW4m0G-v32BXLVN78g5gHbX20dW5VwQ8V97zGtvW89BzFn4RBNqgW86-3Lx4K22V6N12DWlcVyD28W4bscks3P0055W5Ncdj757DHt_W4k3Y4r4Mg1mhW6hCB6R310rNnW2vpzGm4kgzyBW3hP7pz2fx76mW6RdL3m7VZkXXW2y8ksv1Kb3z8W3_grZT4qJNc-N2n6K4lnVT0XM9QnW7t1d6dW3ZQhhg2Wzcp9W6m8blK93VRy-W6SQwdH6TCwg_W6NqrLC6J5